# App Router

- Pages live under `src/app/[locale]/` with next-intl (`en`, `zu`; default `en`).
- Locale prefix: `as-needed` — English at `/`, Zulu at `/zu/...`.
- API routes in `src/app/api/` (not under `[locale]`).
- Prefer Server Components; add `'use client'` only for hooks, events, or browser APIs.
- Co-locate `loading.tsx` where the project already uses it (e.g. contact, projects).
- SEO metadata: follow patterns in `src/app/[locale]/layout.tsx` and `@/utils/seo`.
- Root layout wraps with `NextIntlClientProvider`, `Providers`, and shared `Layout`.
